<div class="component container" id="how-we-help-you" data-nav-item="">
    <div class="component-content" >

<div class="component c-feature-row-teaser">
    <div class="component-content">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-8 col-md-10 off-md-1 col-lg-12 off-lg-2">
                <h2 class="c-feature-row-teaser__header">
                    How we help you
                </h2>
            </div>
        </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-4 col-sm-8 col-md-10 off-md-1 col-lg-12 off-lg-2">
                    <div class="component accordion c-feature-row-teaser__accordion js-feature-row-teaser__accordion">
                        <div class="component-content">
                            <div>
                                <ul class="items">
<li class="item">
    <div class="toggle-header" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="label">
            <h3>
                Are you developing effective creative, and the right media plan?
            </h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rich-text toggle-content toggle-content--reset">
        <div class="row c-feature-row-teaser__main-content">
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-5 col-f-md-5 col-f-lg-7 c-feature-row-teaser__content-desc">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    Opportunity
                </h4>
                <div>
                    Every brand needs to tell its story in a way that engages the right consumers. Gain deep insight into the consumers and shoppers who will deliver the most growth for your brand, and get trusted data and advertising intelligence to support the media planning process. We can provide consumer insight, competitive intelligence, and campaign and creative effectiveness measurement at all stages of the creative process.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-3 off-f-md-1 col-f-md-4 col-lg-3 toggle-content__aside">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    How we help
                </h4>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/advertising-media-pr/consumer-profiling-and-targeting">Consumer Profiling and Targeting</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/advertising-media-pr/advertising-intelligence">Advertising Intelligence</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/advertising-media-pr/creative-development-and-evaluation">Creative Development and Evaluation</a></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</li><li class="item">
    <div class="toggle-header" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="label">
            <h3>
                Can you activate against your media plan?
            </h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rich-text toggle-content toggle-content--reset">
        <div class="row c-feature-row-teaser__main-content">
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-5 col-f-md-5 col-f-lg-7 c-feature-row-teaser__content-desc">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    Opportunity
                </h4>
                <div>
                    Once you understand your target market, make sure you can reach them. Use Kantar insights to identify and segment your ideal audience, then link these to external activation platforms, for much better targeting. Our portfolio of pre-defined audiences (and the ability to create bespoke segments) enables you to be more precise when you advertise online.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-3 off-f-md-1 col-f-md-4 col-lg-3 toggle-content__aside">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    How we help
                </h4>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/advertising-media-pr/programmatic-activation">Programmatic Activation</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/advertising-media-pr/consumer-profiling-and-targeting">Consumer Profiling and Targeting</a></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</li><li class="item">
    <div class="toggle-header" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="label">
            <h3>
                Do you measure media consumption and optimise your communications plan?
            </h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rich-text toggle-content toggle-content--reset">
        <div class="row c-feature-row-teaser__main-content">
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-5 col-f-md-5 col-f-lg-7 c-feature-row-teaser__content-desc">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    Opportunity
                </h4>
                <div>
                    It's crucial to understand how and where your content is being consumed, and the effectiveness of media channels, so you can make improvements in real time. Whether your communications plan involves paid advertising (on digital and traditional channels), PR or social media, we provide the tools you need to understand and address the impact each media channel is having on the brand, on penetration and on sales.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-3 off-f-md-1 col-f-md-4 col-lg-3 toggle-content__aside">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    How we help
                </h4>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/advertising-media-pr/campaign-effectiveness-and-roi">Campaign Effectiveness and ROI</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/audience-measurement">Audience-Measurement</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/onclusive">Earned Media and Reputation Tracking</a></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</li><li class="item">
    <div class="toggle-header" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="label">
            <h3>
                Can you evaluate your creative, media and PR activity, to improve campaigns now and in the future?
            </h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rich-text toggle-content toggle-content--reset">
        <div class="row c-feature-row-teaser__main-content">
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-5 col-f-md-5 col-f-lg-7 c-feature-row-teaser__content-desc">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    Opportunity
                </h4>
                <div>
                    Marketing and PR are ongoing investments, and every campaign activity should be evaluated to assess its impact on brand, sales and reputation. At Kantar, we look at communications activity holistically: proactive and reactive PR, creative content, the effectiveness of media channels and touchpoints, and influencers, to advise on future strategies.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-sm-3 off-f-md-1 col-f-md-4 col-lg-3 toggle-content__aside">
                <h4 class="c-feature-row-teaser__inner-title">
                    How we help
                </h4>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/advertising-media-pr/creative-development-and-evaluation">Creative Development and Evaluation</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/expertise/advertising-media-pr/campaign-effectiveness-and-roi">Campaign Effectiveness and ROI</a></span>
                        <span><a href="/uki/onclusive" target="_blank">Earned Media and Reputation Tracking</a></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</li>                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>


